WEBVTT

00:25:29.434 --> 00:25:31.307
You just needed to be a Rohingya.

00:25:31.331 --> 00:25:34.426
You did not need to be
on Facebook or YouTube

00:25:34.450 --> 00:25:36.450
in Christchurch,
New Zealand, to be dead --

00:25:36.474 --> 00:25:38.633
you just needed to be
in one of those mosques.

00:25:38.657 --> 00:25:41.847
This stuff is affecting people
who are not on these platforms,

00:25:41.871 --> 00:25:43.979
in ways we cannot recover from.

00:25:44.003 --> 00:25:51.003
(Music)